PROBLEM  STATEMENT

As hotel chains consolidate and booking apps and short-term rentals grow, new fees and new restrictions make it tougher to reserve the best rate, and also, As travel websites get bigger, booking a decent hotel room gets harder.
 148.3 million travel bookings are completed online every year. The online travel market projection of $756 billion in 2019 is expected to grow to $817billion by 2020. 15.4% growth in worldwide online travel sales and 10.3%growth in online hotel bookings.
